data.description: Large open concept bi-level in Crown Point! Home features large kitchen with plenty of cabinets, dining room with access to the patio door that leads to a beautiful deck in the backyard. Primary bedroom has walk thru to the primary bathroom. Spacious closets throughout. The lower level features a large rec room, finished laundry room, second bathroom, and another large room. Garage is attached with door opener. Large shed in the backyard for more storage.ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT A 2.875 INTEREST RATE!!!! Schedule your showing today!!
